name: Survio
tag_list: online-surveys, free, survey, questionnaire, online, quiz, quizzes
overview:
Survio online survey tool (survio.com) began as a startup in the Czech Republic and was launched formaly in April 2012.

Survio provides a free and easy tool for any type of online survey. The product provides plenty of ready-made survey templates, layouts and styles. You can easily create a new survey with professional content and a stunning look in just a few clicks! You can view your collected responses in real-time, using tables, charts, PDF reports and data files for most filetypes.

The user interface is extremely easy and intuitive. With Survio anybody can create a survey, even if you have no experience. Users won’t need to download or install anything and Survio can be used with any popular browser. Anyone can have a survey on their own web site or Facebook for free in minutes.
